hopobject.body: Hello good day prescriptiononline.com.au In this photo taken Tuesday, July 9, 2013, Selina Mills, a sea turtle nesting surveyor with the Miami-Dade County Parks, tapes off a sea turtle nesting sight on Haulover Beach in Miami. All sea turtles are protected by the Federal Endangered Species Act. It is against the law to touch or disturb nesting sea turtles, hatchlings, or their nests. Sea turtle nesting season on Florida's Atlantic coast runs from March through October. (AP Photo/Lynne Sladky)
